      <Docs>
        <summary>
            Make <c>^</c>, <c>$</c>, <c>\Z</c>, and <c>.</c> recognize all common newline sequences
            (<c>\r\n</c>, <c>\r</c>, <c>\n</c>, <c>\v</c> (VT), <c>\f</c> (FF), and the Unicode newlines <c>\u0085</c>, <c>\u2028</c>, <c>\u2029</c>)
